Package: ritapi-advanced
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: ARCH_PLACEHOLDER
Maintainer: vadhh <ops@example.com>
Depends: python3.12, adduser
Recommends: redis-server, nginx
Description: Layer-7 API protection service
 RitAPI Advanced is a standalone FastAPI service providing layer-7 API
 protection: WAF, rate limiting, bot detection, injection/exfiltration
 detection, JWT/API-key authentication, and RBAC.
 .
 The package bundles a pre-built Python virtualenv — no pip install
 required on the target host. Redis must be available separately.
